e.";i:44;s:64:"Decorating Chamberlain Garage Door Opener Wall Control Flashing.";i:45;s:53:"Garage Door Remote Repairs Replacements And Upgrades.";i:46;s:373:"Unplug the opener what should be for a good minutein the meantime remove the batteries from the transmitters including the key lessand if you have a battery back-up you would know this that if the house power was cut the garage door could still be openedthere is no battery in the wall transmitterplug back in the opener and replace the batteries which should be freshthen.";i:47;s:71:"Garage door opener works from the wall control but NOT from the remote.";i:48;s:184:"Check all remotes if all the remotes and wireless devices stopped working at the same time this could indicate the circuit board needs replaced Replace the remote battery if neccesary.";}}